353
00:36:19,110 --> 00:36:20,330
[If]

354
00:36:20,980 --> 00:36:22,450
[we can't meet again,]

355
00:36:23,180 --> 00:36:25,050
[I'll remember the
way you look every time]

356
00:36:25,140 --> 00:36:26,480
[you said goodbye to me with a smile.]

