387
00:38:09,170 --> 00:38:10,760
So I bought one for each of you.

388
00:38:11,900 --> 00:38:13,000
Taste it.

389
00:38:13,680 --> 00:38:15,060
Tell me if it's delicious.

390
00:38:16,590 --> 00:38:17,340
But its taste

391
00:38:17,420 --> 00:38:18,850
