00:39:07,870 --> 00:39:08,750
Taste it.

410
00:39:08,950 --> 00:39:09,930
Thank you, aunty.

411
00:39:11,800 --> 00:39:12,730
I think

412
00:39:12,960 --> 00:39:14,390
