413
00:39:14,480 --> 00:39:15,270
How is it?

414
00:39:15,360 --> 00:39:16,320
How about this?

415
00:39:16,400 --> 00:39:17,670
Let's visit the furniture stores while

416
00:39:17,770 --> 00:39:19,510
