00:40:21,380 --> 00:40:23,630
Do you have any
suggestion, old comrade?

443
00:40:26,910 --> 00:40:28,430
Don't drag me into this.

444
00:40:32,770 --> 00:40:34,310
If that's the case,

445
00:40:35,480 --> 00:40:36,450
just mind

