00:40:42,070 --> 00:40:43,370
Let's have a another toast.

450
00:40:44,390 --> 00:40:45,450
Come!

451
00:40:46,190 --> 00:40:47,100
Xia Chu,

452
00:40:47,180 --> 00:40:48,210
thank you.

