475
00:41:34,750 --> 00:41:36,130
Prepare to fight!

476
00:41:37,650 --> 00:41:38,710
[Here]

477
00:41:38,820 --> 00:41:40,490
[we fight like the scorching sun.]

478
00:41:40,580 --> 00:41:41,920
[We become stronger.]

479
00:41:42,620 --> 00:41:43,640
[Here]

